ZH: 请你说明你的疑惑。
EN: Please explain your confusion.

ZH: 这份报告需再说明一下。
EN: This report needs further clarification.

ZH: 他正在说明昨天发生的情况。
EN: He is explaining what happened yesterday.

ZH: 我需要说明一下我没收到你的邮件。
EN: I need to clarify that I did not receive your email.

ZH: 请问，你可以说明这个概念吗？
EN: Can you explain this concept, please?

ZH: 他拒绝说明他的行为原因。
EN: He refuses to explain his actions.

ZH: 我们要求他们说明他们的决定。
EN: We asked them to explain their decision.

ZH: 请说明您的法律权利。
EN: Please explain your legal rights.

ZH: 这篇文章需要说明它的观点。
EN: This article needs to explain its point of view.

ZH: 她在说明如何正确使用这个软件。
EN: She is explaining how to use this software correctly.

ZH: 这张地图没有说明道路类型。
EN: This map does not indicate road types.

ZH: 我需要说明一下我为什么晚到。
EN: I need to explain why I was late.

ZH: 请你说明为什么这项决定如此重要。
EN: Please explain why this decision is so important.

ZH: 我们需要说明项目的目标和目的。
EN: We need to explain the goals and objectives of the project.

ZH: 他不愿意说明他的选择背后的原因。
EN: He is unwilling to explain the reasons behind his decisions.

ZH: 我需要说明一下我对这个问题的看法。
EN: I need to explain my perspective on this issue.

ZH: 这篇文章没有充分说明作者的思想。
EN: This article does not fully explain the author's ideas.

ZH: 请说明您的需求，我们会尽力满足。
EN: Please explain your needs, and we will do our best to meet them.

ZH: 他没有给出详细的说明。
EN: He did not provide a detailed explanation.

ZH: 这本书没有明确说明作者的立场。
EN: This book does not clearly indicate the author's position.
